dc_description_s: Panama Years Of Study Census Data, 2010 is a polygon theme representing Manzanas (6th level administrative units) in Panama as of 2010. This map is georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. Attribute data include summary results of the 2010 Panamanian census questions regarding years of study. The documentation of these variables can be found in the "LP09" section from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Panama 2010 Census collection.
dc_title_s: Panama Years Of Study Census Data, 2010
